sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant Gateway as Nginx gateway
    participant Outpost as authentik outpost
    participant Auth as authentik
    participant Surface as Protected surface

    Browser->>Gateway: GET protected URL
    Gateway->>Outpost: auth_request with cookies
    Outpost-->>Gateway: 401 when no valid session
    Gateway-->>Browser: Redirect to authentik login flow
    Browser->>Auth: Login or upstream SSO
    Auth-->>Browser: Session cookie
    Browser->>Gateway: Retry protected URL
    Gateway->>Outpost: auth_request with session cookie
    Outpost-->>Gateway: 204 plus X-authentik identity headers
    Gateway->>Surface: Proxy request with trusted identity context
